<view class="page safe-bottom">
  <view class="hero card">
    <view class="hero-copy">
      <text class="eyebrow">今天先不买</text>
      <text class="h1">今天差点买什么？</text>
      <text class="muted">先选一个类型。名称和金额都可以不填。</text>
    </view>
    <image class="hero-img" src="/runtime-assets/brand/mascot-pause.png" mode="aspectFit" />
  </view>

  <view class="pause-guide section">选类型 → 先放一放 → 到时间回来决定买不买</view>

  <view class="option-grid section">
    <button
      class="option {{selectedId === item.id ? 'active' : ''}}"
      wx:for="{{pauseOptions}}"
      wx:key="id"
      bindtap="selectOption"
      data-id="{{item.id}}"
    >
      <image class="option-icon" src="{{item.iconPath}}" mode="aspectFit" />
      <text class="option-title">{{item.label}}</text>
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card section">
    <view class="row-between">
      <text class="h2">想补充一点吗？</text>
      <text class="pill">全都可不填</text>
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">具体想买什么</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="例如：奶茶、耳机、通勤包" value="{{name}}" bindinput="onNameInput" maxlength="40" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">大概金额</text>
      <input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="可选" value="{{amount}}" bindinput="onAmountInput" />
    </view>
    <button class="primary-btn submit" bindtap="submitPause">先不买，放进冷静箱</button>
    <text class="submit-note">不填也可以，只在这台设备保存一条暂停记录。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="daily card section">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view>
        <text class="eyebrow">最近记录</text>
        <text class="daily-title">{{todayDone ? '今天已经暂停过一次' : '今天还没有暂停记录'}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="daily-count">{{stats.cooling}} 待决定</text>
    </view>
    <view class="dot-row">
      <view class="dot {{index < weeklyDots ? 'done' : ''}}" wx:for="{{dotList}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
    <text class="muted">想买时先记一下，到时间回来选“没买”或“买了”就好。</text>
  </view>
</view>
